• Raises concerns about low domestic gas utilisation as penetration remains below 20% The Federal Government, through the Department of the Petroleum Resources (DPR), yesterday, said it is yet to issue guidelines on the proposed bid rounds in Nigeria’s marginal oil fields, adding that such exercise cannot be done in secrecy.
  
